text: Moodswing is the 2003 album by Kacy Crowley. It was released independently and is popular in Crowley's hometown of Austin, Texas. == Track listing == # "Everything" # "Kind of Perfect" # "Unrecovered" # "Ashes" # "Suspended" # "Holding in the World" # "Blood" # "Church Organ" # "Traffic" # "Humble Beginnings" ==References== Category:2003 albums Category:Kacy Crowley albums
